Name: Climb With Wheelbarrow
About the game: Climb With Wheelbarrow is a game in which you will climb up with a wheelbarrow using the forces of a blue man. The floor can be anything: tables, chairs, barrels, boxes, bottles, sofas and so on. Get to the top as quickly as possible, losing a minimum of bricks and show the best result! Why do you need this? I do not know. But I'm sure that there are players who will like such tests.
